{
  "stem": "15686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would what you call today mug us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In other words, they would look for our pocket money and take it and things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember, to give you an instance-- this was later on around 1937, '38-- I was studying for my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had to go to the home of our Cantor that was going to teach me how to do what I had to do.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were some kids-- my age, not much older-- who knew that a Cantor lived there, because the Cantor was very proud, and he had his name on a brass plate with the title Cantor underneath.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And these Hitler Youth children knew that Jewish boys would come there regularly, one every hour during the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they would beat us up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if you denied that you were Jewish or tried to, they would go through your pockets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if you were carrying a kippah or anything like that, they would really become quite cruel, as children can be, both physically and-- abusive-- and verbally.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was a gradual thing, which degenerated from just ignoring us to actually becoming physical and making life a little tough.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the elementary school years, well, as I said, we played all the children's games.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sports was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sports were organized by the schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans, both Jews and Gentiles, put a lot of emphasis on physical education in the schools.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would have physical ed every other day or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The school had a gym.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were certain swimming pools, which Jews were allowed to use in the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only one or two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That started about 1937.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
